If you are Manta Stakers and want to bridge your Manta from Atlantic to Pacific. 
If you cannot see your assets on Manta Pacific after bridging from https://app.manta.network/, your assets are not gone. They are likely on Moonbeam, which is the intermediary chain for bridging assets over to Manta Pacific.

2/2 

If your assets arrive on and remain on Moonbeam while bridging, you can go to https://cbridge.celer.network/ -- from there, select Moonbeam as the source chain and Pacific as the destination chain. You should see your Manta in the Celer app after selecting Moonbeam as the source chain (as xcManta).

Please note that you will need GLMR to pay gas on Moonbeam in order to move the Manta tokens.

Meanwhile, the team is working on a fix for the bridge bug on https://app.manta.network/
